'''Dysorthography''' is a specific [[dysgraphia|dysgraphic]] disorder of spelling which accompanies [[dyslexia]] by a direct consequence of the phonological disorder.<ref>{{Cite book| publisher = Institut national de la santé et de la recherche médicale| last = Centre| first = INSERM Collective Expertise| title = Dyslexia Dysorthography Dyscalculia| accessdate = 2016-08-02| date = 2007| url = https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK10787/| pmid = 21348173}}</ref>

